text:
(白夜)「📱何を勝手に話してるのかな？」
(瑞希)「白夜、、、猫耳メイド服着てくれたら猫カフェに連れて行ってあげる」
(白夜)「📱猫カフェ、、、、、、行きたいけど、、、猫耳メイド服、、、、、、絶対に連れて行ってよ」
(杏)「それでいいんだスイーツ好きなら家の店においでよ美味しいスイーツたくさんあるよ」
(白夜)「📱今度場所教えて絶対に行く」
trans:
(Byakuya) "📱What are you talking about without my permission?"
(Mizuki) "Byakuya... If you wear a cat-ear maid outfit, I will take you to a cat cafe."
(Byakuya) "📱A cat cafe... I want to go, but... a cat-ear maid outfit... You definitely have to take me there."
(An) "If that is the case and you like sweets, come to my shop. We have lots of delicious sweets."
(Byakuya) "📱Tell me the location next time. I will definitely go."
